parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Warning Light Illumination and Failure to Deploy
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the seatbelt light stays on even when the seatbelt is fastened
the airbag light comes on and goes off intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Takata Airbag Recall and Parts Unavailability
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has left many vehicles without a functioning airbag system, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the vehicle is under recall but parts are not available
the manufacturer has exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle control can cause the vehicle to stall or decelerate suddenly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The electronic throttle control light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or decelerates suddenly
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
the vehicle idles high or rough
the vehicle is unable to reach normal speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the integrated control module can cause various electrical systems to malfunction, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the windshield wipers fail to work
the vehicle stalls or decelerates suddenly
the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the total integrated power module can cause the vehicle to stall or decelerate suddenly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or decelerates suddenly
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
the vehicle is unable to restart without charging the battery overnight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brakes squeak
the vehicle fails to stop when applying the brakes
the brake system warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various electrical components to malfunction, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The speedometer fails
the vehicle's electrical systems malfunction
the vehicle's warning lights come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall, lose acceleration, and experience erratic shifting, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The throttle body warning message illuminates
the vehicle stalls
the engine RPM decreases
the vehicle loses acceleration
and the electronic throttle control light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Control Module (TCM) and Powertrain Control Module (PCM) Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM and PCM can cause the vehicle to experience erratic shifting, lose acceleration, and stall, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts hard
has a delay in accelerating
the check engine light illuminates
and the vehicle loses acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front wheel bearing can cause the vehicle to experience unusual noises, affect the brakes, and lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The front end of the vehicle makes popping and creaking noises
and the wheel bearing is faulty.
